npm install --save-dev nodemon

make sure mongodb is installed and up and running

To start API server

	nodemon sr-api-server.js


To Test API, use postman

http://localhost:3000/devices [GET] -> lists all devices

http://localhost:3000/devices [POST] -> insert a device

header key : DeviceName and  Value :<>

use x-www-form-urlencoded
